'''Child saints''' are [[child]]ren and [[adolescent]]s who died or were [[martyr]]ed and have been declared [[saint]]s or [[martyr]]s of the [[Roman Catholic]], [[Eastern Orthodox]], [[Coptic Orthodox]], [[Anglican]], [[Episcopal Church (United States)|Episcopalian]], or [[Lutheran]] Churches or have been beatified or venerated by those churches.
