a/ Blessed Panacea de'Muzzi of Quarona]</ref> * [[Pancras of Rome]] * [[Paola Renata Carboni]]<ref name="sai" /> * [[Justus and Pastor|Pastor]] * [[Pedro Calungsod]] * [[Pelagius of Constance]] * [[Pelagius of Cordova]] * [[Peter the Aleut]] * [[Philomena]] * [[Saint Ponticus|Ponticus]]<ref>[http://www.catholic.org/saints/saint.php?saint_id=5560 St. Pothinus]</ref><ref>[http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-503253/Italian-girl-died-aged-set-youngest-saint-Vatican.html Italian girl who died aged six is set to be made youngest ever saint by Vatican]</ref><ref>[http://www.phatmass.com/phorum/index.php?s=3d6361ee5ac851f2c01226c94794f29c&showtopic=2105&mode=linearplus History: 2nd Century – Phatmass Phorum – Catholic Forum and Community]</ref> * [[Saint Prisca|Prisca]] * [[Quiricus and Julietta|Quiricus (Cyr, Cyricus)]] * [[Rachele Noceti]]<ref name="k18" /> * [[Rachelina Ambrosini]]<ref name="sai" /><ref name="xl4" /> * [[Saint Rais|Rais]] * [[Ramón Montero Navarro]]<ref name="sai" /><ref name="n44" /> * [[Rebeca Rocamora Nadal]]<ref>[http://newsaints.faithweb.com/year/1996.htm ~1996~]</ref> * [[Saint Reparata|Reparata]] * [[Richard of Pontoise]]<ref>{{it icon}} [http://www.santiebeati.it/dettaglio/93675 Saint Richard of Pontoise]</ref><ref name="bld">[http://www.romancatholicism.org/leese-church.htm The Attitude of the Catholic Church towards Jewish Ritual Murder]</ref> * [[Rose of Viterbo]] * [[Rudolph of Berne]]<ref name="bld" /><ref>{{it icon}} [http://www.santiebeati.it/dettaglio/90856 Blessed Rudolph of Berne]</ref> * [[Rumwold of Buckingham|Rumwold]] * [[Solange]] of Bourges<ref>[http://saints.sqpn.com/saint-solange-of-bourges/ Saint Solange of Bourges]</ref> * [[Stanislaus Kostka]] * [[Tarcisius]] * [[Teresa Bracco]]<ref name="n44" /> * [[Teresa of the Andes|Teresa of Los Andes]] * [[Theresa of Jesus]]<ref>{{it icon}} [http://www.santiebeati.it/dettaglio/93698 Blessed Theresa of Jesus]</ref> * [[Tremorus of Brittany]]<ref>[http://saints.sqpn.com/saint-tremorus